#Bookstore Database Management System
## Project Overview
This project is a Bookstore Database Management System developed using MySQL Workbench
Designed to manage bookstore data efficiently.

## Dataset
The project uses the following CSV files:
-Books.csv
-Customers.csv
-Orders.csv

## Tools used
-MySQL
-MySQL Workbench
-GitHub(for project hosting) 

